Package org.gvsig.personaldb

PersonalDB library API.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    PersonalDBManager
    This class is responsible of the management of the library's business logic.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    PersonalDBLibrary
    Library for PersonalDB API initialization and configuration.
    PersonalDBLocator
    This locator is the entry point for the PersonalDB library, providing access to all PersonalDB services through the PersonalDBManager .
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    DataServerExplorerParametersException
    Exception thrown when there is an error creating a connection to the personal database.
    DBAccessException
    Exception thrown when there is an error creating a connection to the personal database.
    PersonalDBException
    Generic exception thrown in the PersonalDB API when the exception or error may be dealt by the program or the user of the program which is a client of the PersonalDB API.

Package org.gvsig.personaldb Description

PersonalDB library API.

It allows to get new PersonalDB and get their text.
